  "title": "DecisionArtifactType — schema mapping",
  "description": "Canonical mapping from DecisionArtifactType enum values to the JSON Schema relpath that defines the corresponding artifact shape. When an AuditRow.decisionRef.artifactType is X, the artifact at decisionRef.artifactId MUST validate against schemas/{mapping[X]}. Consumers should resolve via this mapping rather than inferring from convention.",
